  "design_goals": [
    "Keep ontology limited to DART-common financial concepts and document priors.",
    "Avoid benchmark-shaped metric families and question-specific formulas.",
    "Let the planner infer arithmetic composition from user intent and concept mentions.",
    "Keep parser output generic and bind concept selection through lightweight priors only."
